snippet.textDisplay: I cannot understand Sindhi, but Aayi Aayi touched my heart. You don't need to understand a language to know the emotion behind the song, and this song made me feel a deep connection to Sindh and its people. Jug jug jiyo Noman sahab, you are a wonderful artist. By God, you made me fall in love with Sindh and made me proud to call myself Pakistani.
